Getting 5 squad on SoT.  It's difficult, but doable.

You have to find another ship on the server you can talk to. Many ships you can just use proximity voice chat, but sometimes people can't use proximity chat, so you should always try typing in text chat if they are unresponsive. But there are people who turn all chat off, so just be aware that some people will not hear you or respond to you no matter what.

Once you find someone who you can speak with on your server, then you simply have to ask them to friend and invite someone from your boat into their game. Whoever they invite will be on their ship, and then the person who invited them can stay and join in, or simply log off, but so long as the ship still has a crew member (the person who was originally on your ship), the ship will remain.

It requires a long term gameplan to get working, but you can absolutely get it going and it's hysterical.
